powerpc/mm: Move pgtable_t into platform headers

This patch move pgtable_t into platform headers.

It gets rid of the CONFIG_PPC_64K_PAGES case for PPC64
as nohash/64 doesn't support CONFIG_PPC_64K_PAGES.

